# Introduction to Generative AI

## What is Generative AI?

Generative AI refers to AI systems that can create new content instead of only analysing existing data.
This content can include text, code, images, audio, or structured information.

Rather than following predefined rules, Generative AI learns patterns from large datasets and generates outputs based on context.
In modern software, it acts as a flexible intelligence layer embedded inside products and workflows.

