## What is an LLM?

A Large Language Model (LLM) is a type of Generative AI trained on very large amounts of text data.
Its main task is to predict the next token based on context.

Despite this simple objective, LLMs can perform complex tasks such as reasoning, summarisation, translation, and code generation.
They are the core engine behind most modern Generative AI applications.

